commit 26f5ae0d61c7a3c5212873d726a437e349df8191
Author: John Griffith <john.griffith@solidfire.com>
Date:   Mon Sep 24 12:59:15 2012 -0600

    Add missing entries in setup, fix up pip-requires
    
